PTX PC-bar-sync
"Producer-Consumer pattern using named barriers.
 Arrive does not block P1.
 Load and store are not ordered."
{
x=0;
P0:r0=0
}
 P0@cta 0,gpu 0   | P1@cta 0,gpu 0   ;
 st.weak x, 1     |                  ;
 bar.cta.sync 0   | bar.cta.sync 0   ;
                  | ld.weak r0, x   ;
forall
 (P1:r0 == 1)